{"tid":1791784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武「中環OL」同朋友發起義賣利是封活動","createTime":"2019-12-21T06:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:17:06.000Z","uid":279009,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20f6f232c4a9d45b4e3feabff57520e725533e9f","tid":1791784,"uid":279009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"Facebook page:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=108917943946253&amp;id=108110387360342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D108917943946253%26id%3D108110387360342&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e29a4d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=108917943946253&amp;id=108110387360342</a><br />\n<br />\n全文如下：<br />\n&lt;義賣新年利是封&gt;<br />\n各位香港人好，我們是幾位包括「中環OL」在內組成的朋友，希望透過義賣利是封，幫助港外的香港人。<br />\n我們由2014年認識黄國桐律師至今，知道黄律師一直盡心協力去幫助每一位港內及海外手足。目前黄律師正在發起「保護傘」計劃，希望協助居台港人。有見及此，我們希望作為一個愛惜港人的香港人，可以盡點綿力，協助推動「保護傘」計劃。<br />\n(有關「保護傘」計劃的報導連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191217/60386966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60386966&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=4c66e5e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60386966&h=3cbbc91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191217/60386966</a>)<br />\n是次「義賣利是封」並不是一個眾籌活動，而是義賣產品及扣除所需之印刷成本後，再將所有利潤捐獻出去。<br />\n為了增加透明度及讓公眾了解義賣進度，我們將會每日在專頁內更新收到的訂單數量，並由專業會計師處理所有帳目。義賣完結後所收到之款項總額，會連同相關印刷單據，刊登在本專頁上。<br />\n希望「中環人」的力量，能connect同樣為香港人的你和我，一同為香港集氣!<br />\n<br />\n利是封價目：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGvsecb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGvsecb.png&h=9556801f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/21/142738_d6fa2b49bcc254a81ff334649b6fe1bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F21%2F142738_d6fa2b49bcc254a81ff334649b6fe1bf.jpg&h=cbcf00cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVRSqiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVRSqiS.jpg&h=163f2b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkzgRYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkzgRYS.jpg&h=c7b0aae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2FcqiT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2FcqiT.jpg&h=248c432e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n款式一：「中環OL」<br />\nSize：90 x 168mm 長形利是封<br />\n描述：雙面印刷，前頁「勇」字及後頁「香港人反抗」字體燙金<br />\n價錢：$50/5個<br />\n<br />\n款式二：「眼神Pepe」<br />\nSize：90 x 90mm 方形利是封<br />\n描述：單面印刷，粉紅色底，Pepe眼神最殺食，期待有日大家「煲底見」!<br />\n價錢：$50/10個<br />\n<br />\n款式三：「光復香港連登豬」<br />\nSize：90 x 90mm 方形利是封<br />\n描述：單面印刷，黄色底，代表香港的連登豬，寫上「光復香港，時代革命」，「Fight for Freedom，Stand with Hong Kong」及「五大訴求，缺一不可」!<br />\n價錢：$50/10個<br />\n<br />\n款式四：「五大素球黃頭盔」<br />\nSize：90 x 90mm 方形利是封<br />\n描述：單面印刷，紅色底，代表香港抗爭初的黄頭盔食著素球麵，「五大訴求，缺一不可」，「Five Demands Not One Less」!<br />\n價錢：$50/10個<br />\n<br />\n款式五：「抗爭女神年曆卡」<br />\nSize：A5<br />\n描述：單面印刷，2020年年曆卡，以抗爭女神為背景，年曆卡上方為一對勇敢為孩子走出來的抗爭父母<br />\n價錢：$20/個<br />\n<br />\n購買一套四款利是封：<br />\n中環OL：$50/5個<br />\n眼神Pepe：$50/10個<br />\n光復香港連登豬：$50/10個<br />\n五大素球黃頭盔：$50/10個<br />\n合共$200/套 加送抗爭女神年曆卡一張<br />\n<br />\n如欲購買，請pm專頁，並填上：<br />\n1. 閣下稱呼<br />\n2. 訂購數量<br />\n3. 選擇之pickup point (我們將在1月16日至22日，在葵涌，旺角及中環設立pickup point派發)<br />\n專頁在收到上述資料後，會pm各位入數方法<br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝：<br />\n「中環OL」：原作者Smalltung授權印刷及designer 小虎後期製作<br />\n「眼神Pepe」及「光復香港連登豬」：Designer ROU設計<br />\n「五大素球黃頭盔」：原作者Purin及Miss M後期製作<br />\n「抗爭女神年曆卡」：抗爭女神原作者及大眼夫妻後期製作<br />\n<br />\n所有訂單將於12月26日(四)下午6點截單!<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油! 香港人反抗! 香港人報仇!"},{"pid":"5ceb21b2201c78d55f4215a28ef1719caad2edf4","tid":1791784,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"好似幾正"},{"pid":"8356ea8266584010f3479fbd9b30840e8c515c9f","tid":1791784,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47658476a52a1271f7796d2626ce7257b10114f","tid":1791784,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ceb21b2201c78d55f4215a28ef1719caad2edf4","tid":1791784,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"好似幾正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"但係我想知點解利是封會有五個咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fcae7fb5c922bf7cfb15dceef39e75b993283f","tid":1791784,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"支持黃色經濟圈活動<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 <br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默🈲❌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784354</a>"},{"pid":"6d8f9fadd0ba32802c0053796c2f1fe6a1051832","tid":1791784,"uid":253263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47658476a52a1271f7796d2626ce7257b10114f","tid":1791784,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ceb21b2201c78d55f4215a28ef1719caad2edf4","tid":1791784,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"好似幾正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"但係我想知點解利是封會有五個咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo